WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:05.560
Look into the future

2
00:00:05.560 --> 00:00:07.640
What do you imagine yourself doing?

3
00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:10.680
Maybe an architect?

4
00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:13.320
Perhaps a fitness instructor?

5
00:00:13.840 --> 00:00:15.400
A health practitioner

6
00:00:15.400 --> 00:00:17.440
Or even a helicopter pilot

7
00:00:17.800 --> 00:00:21.480
Right now, you might not know
exactly what job is for you

8
00:00:21.480 --> 00:00:22.880
But don’t worry…

9
00:00:22.880 --> 00:00:25.480
Just go to Barclays Lifeskills and register

10
00:00:25.480 --> 00:00:27.840
There you’ll find our Wheel of Strengths

11
00:00:27.840 --> 00:00:31.240
A tool to help you find
a career that suits you

12
00:00:31.240 --> 00:00:32.640
It’s simple…

13
00:00:32.640 --> 00:00:36.000
First of all, click the skills
you feel you’re good at

14
00:00:36.440 --> 00:00:38.800
Then choose your interests

15
00:00:38.800 --> 00:00:43.000
And finally think about what
personality traits best describe you.

16
00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:46.240
Then spin the wheel and see what happens!

17
00:00:46.240 --> 00:00:48.040
You’ll be presented with some suggestions

18
00:00:48.040 --> 00:00:52.320
for jobs that suit your skills,
interests and personality traits

19
00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:53.320
And who knows?

20
00:00:53.320 --> 00:00:56.600
You might find the perfect career path for you

21
00:00:56.600 --> 00:00:58.640
A world of possibilities awaits

22
00:00:58.640 --> 00:01:00.120
So, what are you waiting for?

23
00:01:00.120 --> 00:01:01.760
Give it a go.

24
00:01:02.440 --> 00:01:05.480
Click here to find out more about your future.